'''Evans Bobie Opoku''' yɛ Ghanani amanyɔni ne mmarahyɛ baguani wo mmarahyɛ bagua a ɛtɔ so 7 wɔ Ghana adehyeman a ɛtɔ so nnan no mu, a ogyina hɔ ma Asunafo Atifi abatoɔ mpɛsoa so, a ɛwɔ Bono ne Ahafo Mantam mu. Ogyinae wɔ amanyɔkuo New Partriotic Party (NPP) din mu.

== Nhomasua ==
Evans Bobie kura abodin krataa a ɛyɛ Diploma a onyaa firii suapɔn a ɛne University of [[Ghana]] ho.
